{"tid":742453,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"三千鬆四千頭、QHD MON，IPS","createTime":"2018-07-14T14:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T17:05:34.000Z","uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aeacae15a30a91889e35950f10c43a3a1f1ab889","tid":742453,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:28:23.000Z","msg":"喇叭非必須、背脊有窿掛到牆最好(好似大部份都無)，無就另諗辦法，業餘剪片執相多，會睇片睇戲，PC GAME輕度玩玩，MON會經AV功放，PC輸出，要求色靚少少，唔使去到超專業程度，市面香港行貨或者淘貨，有邊幾隻可以選擇？因為我張卡只係Sapphire HD7870 XT 2GB GDDR5，未來兩年估計都唔會升張卡，(唔壞既話)，所以唔會上4K MON，用緊既1080P 27吋LG MON可能先天問題，1080P根本唔適合做到27吋，所以好痛苦用左大半年，真係好想換左佢，有無人比下意見啊！謝過！"},{"pid":"953fe6aacbc5adbba000024da08ae5b4641a1140","tid":742453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:44:29.000Z","msg":"27吋用4K啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都用緊HD7850出4K 60HZ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916c21c79e45b266e3f9b494802b30d7f00a81be","tid":742453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"953fe6aacbc5adbba000024da08ae5b4641a1140","tid":742453,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:44:29.000Z","msg":"27吋用4K啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都用緊HD7850出4K 60HZ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/225249_acc4fb1152ec0ea70557be484b53aac4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F225249_acc4fb1152ec0ea70557be484b53aac4.png&h=686ea3bb&s